sm.sendNext("But I can't just give you a job advancement that easily. I need you to prove yourself worthy of it. Gunslingers use Guns to eliminate oppositions. In order to become a commendable Gunslinger, you'll need to be good with your Gun, right? Prove it to me that you are.")
